        <abstract> 
<p><hi rend="italic">Helix pomatia</hi> is quite healthy after 20 days’ submersion in salt water.</p> 
            <p>On peas, the evidence is on WDF’s side, but CD cannot see how they can avoid being crossed.</p>
            <p>He is working hard, wishes he "could set less value on the bauble fame"; would work as hard, but with less gusto, if he knew his book would be published forever anonymously.</p>
        </abstract>
